Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運中也有推理的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯中複雜的謎團終有撥雲見日的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位警官的命運會如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情問題必須在日落之前解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人的名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在追尋什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣了謊言 今日也欺蒙了你的眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此世紀之初
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切毫無定數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.19,0:00:41.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨自己孤單卻無法哭泣的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.49,0:00:51.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了換取信任的痛楚 潛藏在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.43,0:00:59.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照出的兩人 這是我倆選擇的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這是我唯一的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.72,0:01:06.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔向無垠的陰暗彼端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.18,0:01:13.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰也不知道的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.35,0:01:18.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在奔向不明之地 你唯一的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.31,0:01:21.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照此速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到 你在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.77,0:21:24.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待充滿刺激的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.08,0:21:31.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的一切一定是我最重要的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.55,0:21:43.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕失去 其實我們仍然一無所獲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.45,0:21:51.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這蔚藍的地球上 有無限的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:56.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free 我想感覺到內心的鼓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.48,0:21:57.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.95,0:22:03.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮的情緒飛揚 海天連成一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.85,0:22:13.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望你能用力的抱著我突破重圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.75,0:22:22.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮的情緒飛揚 海天連成一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.66,0:22:32.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望你能用力的抱著我突破重圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小蘭從佐藤警官的同事由美那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道佐藤警官要跟一個素未謀面的男人相親的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.58,0:01:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了 只要一發現狀況不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子就會立刻找個人幫她脫離相親會場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是誰會幫她脫離相親會場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨 當然是高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.45,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子有麻煩 快點去把她搶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊稱她相親的水都樓發生了命案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一把這個短信發到高木警官的手機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定會大驚失色 馬上衝過去救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.48,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們抱著高度的興趣跑到水都樓卻發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他姓白鳥 該不會是警視廳的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 他跟佐藤小姐在白鶴軒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 佐藤警官的相親對象是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點幫我抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是身負重任的高木警官卻遇到了超市搶案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他追蹤搶匪 一直追到公園的廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現三名嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且目擊者的證詞還不一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法確定哪個才是搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 由美是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在手邊在忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.97,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.86,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南拜託我打這通電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南啊 有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建議你先看看你的手機短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再斟酌你現在的狀況就知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我今天只收到了由美發來的短信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.74,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子有麻煩 你就謊稱她相親的水都樓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官去相親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還沒有看到短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你放心 冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離太陽下山還有一點點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相親的地點就在隔壁的杯戶鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽下山怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官剛才已經答應了那個相親對象的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你如果不能在日落之前破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到水都樓那裡去接她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就接受對方的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就請你先把案發的經過詳細的告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.34,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 高木警官 你還在聽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.58,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事戀愛物語4（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我們已經確定搶匪就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.76,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到公園的公廁裡那三個嫌犯之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三個人當中有兩個是男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一位叫做座間弘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.87,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十一歲 沒有工作 身高大概在180公分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿藍色的毛衣 耳朵上戴個耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於另外一個男的 叫紙枝保男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十二歲 是補習班講師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高在170公分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了一件綠色的毛衣 戴了一副眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的女性是越水映子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十八歲 上班族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高大概是160公分 穿著一身黑色的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上戴兩支手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名搶犯在搶劫超市的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭戴安全帽 身穿外套 手上戴著手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把刀亮出來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿張貼著「錢交出來」的白紙要挾店員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他就丟了外套 然後跑進公園的公廁裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.40,0:05:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過傷腦筋的是 目擊者的證詞完全不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公園前面被搶匪撞倒的老人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看到的是個身穿藍衣的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在服裝店裡看到搶匪的女孩說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一堆人群之中 只有搶匪比大家高出一個頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以應該是身高在180公分以上的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還看到他的外套下穿的是綠色的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是咖啡店的老闆卻說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在店門口的時候曾經跟逃走的搶匪擦肩而過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說他的身高大概170公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且外套下面還穿了一件黑色的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.80,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這三個目擊者看到的搶匪特徵都不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒挺有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼有意思啊 工藤老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你就先到那家咖啡店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我跟你說的問問店長 豆原先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道他姓什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前就很熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.45,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 警察先生 怎麼樣 抓到歹徒了沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶店長到外面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.36,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 你要帶我去哪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話就在店裡面說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.12,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴的是太陽眼鏡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想店長戴的眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那種走到室外照射紫外線之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會在15秒鐘之內變色的調光鏡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前認識他的時候都沒有戴眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會懷疑這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 其實這是一副平光眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很有意思 最近才開始戴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你所看到的那個搶匪穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是因為變色鏡片的關係才看成黑色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.72,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過搶匪的身高我可以肯定是在170公分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有個看到他的女孩子說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身高應該在180公分以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子是在哪家店透過玻璃窗看到搶匪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從這家咖啡店往超市走一百公尺的那家服裝店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話請你走到那家店前面好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.79,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說她看到搶匪比行人還高出一個頭對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.11,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那條路正好是地下鐵的出口到公車站之間的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了某些時段走道上就會出現特別多的人潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那裡有很多人過來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你會怎麼通過那個地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是避開人潮穿過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣穿越速度太慢的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會先把路讓開站在邊緣這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子一定是看到搶匪在邊緣上往前跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才以為他的身高在180公分以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯 這就像拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 每片拼圖雖然乍看之下凌亂不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要換個角度再看一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拼成圖案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.70,0:08:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是換成我來拼湊這些目擊證人的證詞的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.11,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為現在還缺少一個不可或缺的棋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南已經去了很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看看他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南會不會是吃壞肚子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上吃了吐司跟荷包蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人我好像…之前見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是弄錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是那個被搶匪撞倒的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的判斷沒有錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老人的證詞就是決定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 工藤老弟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂 你幹嘛這麼熱心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 是小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.32,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 請你再去詳細地問一次那個老人就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你一定會把搶匪找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老人好像是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪是一個在外套下穿著藍色衣服的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只有座間先生穿著藍色的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是看到了耳環 才會認為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他被撞倒的時候還戴著安全帽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能看到他的長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他怎麼說是女人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 距離落日還有四十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點的話 佐藤警官就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他好像說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 我知道搶匪是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看太陽已經快下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官 其實我不是不相信你做的承諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果高木警官趕不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了這場比賽 我想要一個證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.89,0:11:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就相吻當作是個紀念吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要相吻為證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這不過分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果高木警官不能在日落前趕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很快就會結為夫妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過一言既出駟馬難追的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木那個傢伙在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把那個搶匪抓到嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 有沒有查出什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.82,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個目擊者描述的特徵現在還是沒辦法搭起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個說是穿藍衣服的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個說是身穿綠衣身高180公分的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.03,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個說是170公分的黑衣男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼從這三個嫌犯裡面找出那個超市搶匪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有慢慢調查了 反正現在才三點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還多的是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託有沒有搞錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手錶是不是壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經四點半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪果然是你沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店的店長會說搶匪穿的是黑衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.35,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是因為他戴了變色的調光鏡片看搶匪的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於那個女孩子會認為搶匪有180公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為搶匪把人行道讓開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走道的邊緣奔馳的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黑衣和180公分這兩個證詞去除之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.98,0:13:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把他們兩個人看到的搶匪特徵拼湊起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以知道搶匪是170公分上下身穿綠衣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這名搶匪就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.69,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被搶匪撞倒的老人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是身穿藍衣的女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.03,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們卻忘記了做這項證詞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個平常就戴慣老花眼鏡的老人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來看看 美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的夕陽真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離太陽下山還有大概20分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家的確是常常會把綠色說成是藍綠色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老一輩的人會把藍色 水藍色跟藍綠色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都用藍色來做一種通稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我想到他這個補習班講師說過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給了我一個靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果上課還會特別叫學生不要去注意時間的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.57,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該會把自己手錶的表面放在手腕內側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來上課的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有他自己知道時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.81,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.15,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老人一定是看到他把手錶表面朝手腕內側放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會誤以為他是女人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想他是怕每次上課都要轉過去太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會在平時就這麼戴著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那三個目擊者所描述的特徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.49,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都證明了你就是那個搶劫超市的搶匪 紙枝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就剩下十分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子這場打賭我真的是贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不要這麼難過好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逼你馬上嫁給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你把心情整頓好之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對有耐心等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我向來是站在你這邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官 我是高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才已經揪出那個超市的搶匪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家餐廳距離這裡還挺近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概用五分鐘就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你還不快點到這裡來接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能先問你一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會選我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會相信我 跟對方做這麼大一個賭注呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然是認為你一定會到這裡來接我回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.35,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…這也就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…佐藤警官你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那你對我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.29,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟超市搶匪 到底誰比較重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 去追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 他現在如果再去追搶匪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.16,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是我的命我就認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也許是老天對我擅自拿他來做賭注的懲罰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過賭注就是賭注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們快點開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要做個紀念嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午4點56分 逮捕到搶匪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.07,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 我是…真的需要錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個女人纏著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有付錢才能擺脫她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.28,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了 這裡距離水都樓又有一段距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒希望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好棒 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 我還是放走了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡面真正想要掌握住的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 要親就快點親啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她根本不情願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用勉強了 美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就這樣暫時冷靜一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在再也沒有什麼能夠阻撓我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們馬上就要親吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.73,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別亂來好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會出事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會負責把他帶回警局的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 你就快點去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得像一個警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要期限還沒有到你就不能放棄希望 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 太陽就快下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在好多了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.06,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.28,0:19:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然在不知不覺中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心裡佔了這麼重要的份量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在才發現這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還做什麼刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該是辭職的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.72,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤美和子警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉在你放假的時候打擾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事情了 可以請你來支援我辦案嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.07,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個壞事的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.14,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.24,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.39,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官他剛才已經從走廊那邊往玄關的方向跑走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.25,0:20:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.03,0:21:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 太陽已經完全下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:22:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.92,0:23:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 還不快點上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.01,0:23:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.47,0:23:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有案子對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.79,0:23:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了半天還是得讓我出面幫他的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.10,0:23:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過再回頭看看他們這兩個糊塗的網中人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真讓人有種處境對換的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.26,0:23:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.93,0:23:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是對不起白鳥警官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩的金額是10億元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.46,0:23:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.86,0:23:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.30,0:23:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺 這張畫借我 我一定會還給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.87,0:24:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說只要知道這是什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道秋夫被關在什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.92,0:24:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.11,0:24:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫圖中的綁架者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.85,0:24:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.38,0:24:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.53,0:24:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是10月8日播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.85,0:24:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的體育節 偵探團大活躍
